 can\ncause filamentary structures to appear. Such apparent filaments can also be\ntraced, using the same methodology, in simple simulated maps consisting of\nrandomly placed cores. They have profile shapes similar to observed filaments\nand contain most of the simulated cores.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Aug 2014 20:05:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Feb 2016 12:33:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-04"}
